 reconcile<br>To the idea I could I be so vile<br>So I ignore the trial of my amorality<br>And make pleasant things for inside a gallery<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\n Old white womenThe few, the proudDefending us all whenThere\u2019s a hateful crowd <\/p>\n<p> O, the venerable old white womenThey like pleasant thingsSold with old white man\u2019s acumenA painting, a potting, a poem to sing <\/p>\n<p> They fill up the galleries and boards,the gardens, the place of their choiceThey fill all the platforms in hoardsTo [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":3732,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[36],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-5781","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-poetry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/ianrandmckenzie.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5781","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/ianrandmckenzie.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/ianrandmckenzie.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/ianrandmckenzie.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/ianrandmckenzie.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=5781"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/ianrandmckenzie.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5781\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/ianrandmckenzie.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3732"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/ianrandmckenzie.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=5781"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/ianrandmckenzie.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=5781"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/ianrandmckenzie.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=5781"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}